data.description: Nestled amidst the serene countryside, this stunning POOL home, built in 2018, offers an idyllic escape for those seeking tranquility and contemporary living. Set on an expansive 9.6-ACRE estate, this property perfectly balances open space and modern comfort. Step inside and be welcomed by the spacious and airy open-concept design. The heart of this home is a sprawling living area that seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, making it perfect for family gatherings and entertaining guests. The home's design embraces a modern aesthetic with clean lines, sleek finishes, and abundant natural light. Large windows frame picturesque views of the surrounding countryside, bringing the beauty of the outdoors inside. The chef's kitchen is a masterpiece, featuring high-end stainless steel appliances, including a double wall oven - complimented by a smooth top stove, granite countertops, and ample storage space. It's the perfect place to unleash your culinary creativity. The spacious main suite offers a private retreat with a luxurious en-suite bathroom, complete with a soaking tub, a walk-in tile shower, and a walk-in closet. Step outside onto the expansive deck, perfect for alfresco dining, and take in the breathtaking views of your 9.6 acres of land. The highlight of the outdoor space is undoubtedly the sparkling saltwater pool—a refreshing oasis on hot summer days. Cultivate the existing pecan, apple, pear, peach, cherry trees, and blueberry and blackberry bushes, or create your own mini-farm. Build additional structures, or enjoy the vast open space and privacy of country living. This property is situated in a serene countryside setting, providing a quiet and peaceful retreat from the hustle and bustle of city life. Yet, it's conveniently located within a short drive to essential amenities, schools, and entertainment options. Extras include; a pole barn, outside storage shed, and gated access via Eagle Dr. for a shorter trip into Milton.
